            "id": 6432464,
            "title": "盤中速報 - 迪爾(DE-US)大跌5%，報562.33美元",
            "description": "<main class=\"c1tt5pk2\" id=\"article-container\" style=\"--c1tt5pk2-0:20px\"><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)截至台北時間25日03:54股價下跌29.62美元，報562.33美元，跌幅5%，成交量781,061（股），盤中最高價588.18美元、最低價562.33美元。</p></section><p></p><section style=\"margin-top:30px\"><p><em>美股指數盤中表現</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/DJI\">道瓊指數</a>：-0.16%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/INX\">S&amp;P 500</a>指數：+0.78%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/IXIC\">NASDAQ</a>指數：+1.6%</li><li><a href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/index/GI/SOX\">費城半導體</a>指數：+4.07%</li></ul></section><section><p><em>迪爾(<a data-ga-click-item=\"USS:DE:STOCK:COMMON\" data-ga-event-name=\"Click_Quote\" data-ga-section=\"News_Article_文中行情\" data-ga-target=\"news\" href=\"https://invest.cnyes.com/usstock/detail/DE\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" target=\"_self\">DE-US</a>)歷史漲跌幅</em></p></section><section style=\"margin-top:20px\"><ul> <li>近 1 週：+1.33%</li> <li>近 1 月：+4.03%</li> <li>近 3 月：+15.07%</li> <li>近 6 月：+26.1%</li> <li>今年以來：+27.15%</li></ul></section></main>",
